<div id="preamble-block_60509b0a1914c" class="block-preamble"><p>There’s a lot to think about when running an e-commerce business. </p>
</div>






<p>Your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">marketing strategy</a> is one of the biggest aspects. You can have an entire marketing strategy planned to the point to gain new customers. But what is that worth if you aren’t also working on customer retention?</p>



<p>Keeping up with your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">e-commerce email marketing</a> best practices is the key to maintaining customer relationships that will generate ROI in the long run.</p>



<p>In this article, we’ll go over the most important e-commerce email marketing best practices for 2021.</p>


