<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>The 11 Best Easter Email Examples We&#8217;ve Seen</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-118218" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Easter-Email-Examples-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_6049f9c2ac384" class="block-preamble"><p>Spring is just around the corner, and so is Easter.</p>
</div>






<p>When it comes to e-commerce, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-marketing-strategies&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037719000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1izK4aCXdeQg6Si23k6yGh" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">holidays</a> are a great excuse to run sale campaigns and promote your online store with a hint of festivity. Easter is no exception to this rule.</p>



<p>Often signaling the beginning of <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/spring-email-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037719000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1PO-4DMM1YOBLyyQjTFS9S" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">spring</a>, the Easter holiday is the perfect time to engage your subscribers with colorful, merry emails and invite them to your website.</p>



<p>To help prepare your <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037720000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1SlPzAINNEC_wmopBmpDgI" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email marketing</a> for this holiday season, I took a deep dive into my inbox and put together the 11 best Easter email examples I’ve seen—all from top e-commerce brands, broken down into six strategies.</p>



<p>Let’s get crackin’. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f423.png" alt="🐣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>


