<h2 id="h.2tsyaxe2ucj1"><strong>Table of Contents</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Promote Relevant Products</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Run an Easter Sale</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Offer a Limited-Time Deal</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Throw an Easter Egg Hunt</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Suggest Gift Options</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Engage Your Email List</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Promote Relevant Products</strong></h2>



<p>Although Easter is commonly associated with eggs and bunnies, you don’t necessarily need to sell Easter-themed products to leverage this holiday.</p>



<p>If you’re selling products or offering solutions that can help prospects enjoy this holiday better, use them in your emails and frame them around Easter.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.crateandbarrel.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037721000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2u1-76RZtim_Do9HsJUIv4" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Crate and Barrel</a> is one company that does this right. Check out this email they send with the <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037722000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0Gqql9Htxapckp8GL6LZjP" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">subject line</a> “Ready for Easter? We are. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f423.png" alt="🐣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />”:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="587" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-587x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118221" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-587x1024.png 587w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-172x300.png 172w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-380x663.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-600x1047.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-20x35.png 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-29x50.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-281x490.png 281w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-220x384.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8-385x672.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-8.png 612w" sizes="(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px" /></figure>



<p>Even before you open its email, Crate and Barrel make you reconsider if you’re ready for the holiday ahead. In the email, the company suggests that you already plan for your Easter table and <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037722000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1Ka_f6kuABIj6EVblAUXVp" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">recommends its relevant products</a> to help you do so:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="435" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-435x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118222" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-435x1024.png 435w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-128x300.png 128w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-380x894.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-600x1412.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-15x35.png 15w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-21x50.png 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-208x490.png 208w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-220x518.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7-385x906.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-7.png 641w" sizes="(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px" /></figure></div>



<p>Crate and Barrel are aware that you’ll celebrate this holiday (and the arrival of <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/spring-subject-lines&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037723000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3P4NvxU-X_xFJwtFNZsi7H" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">spring</a>) at home with close family only. That’s why they give you five tips to get ready for Easter, as well as enjoy being home.</p>



<p>Each tip includes one of the company’s products and links that take you to its <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037724000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0o8bspuqLtNUQpod1Dq626" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product pages</a>. It’s a perfect disguise for <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-marketing&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037724000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3vQbw5WmBq7HM1WOiw3Xup" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product marketing</a> while being helpful and relevant to subscribers.</p>



<p>If you’re looking for an even quicker way to promote your products around Easter, you can take inspiration from <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.westelm.co.uk/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037725000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3qa-oY0jZJ2-zUhgNn7lWJ" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">West Elm</a>:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="920" height="980" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118223" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3.png 920w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-282x300.png 282w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-768x818.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-380x405.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-600x639.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-760x810.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-47x50.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-460x490.png 460w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-220x234.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image14-3-385x410.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px" /></figure>



<p><br>Sent with the subject line “Get Easter ready with 20% off dining styles <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f374.png" alt="🍴" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />” West Elm’s email is easy to replicate. Other than the word&nbsp;<em>Easter&nbsp;</em>added to the subject field, the company’s offer is just a regular sale. However, since West Elm cleverly puts it in the holiday frame, it gives you a reason to shop the sale: being ready for Easter.</p>



<p>It’s a smart addition you can use in your sale subject lines in this season, especially if your products aren’t necessarily Easter material.</p>



<p>In the remainder of the email, the company cross-sells with items from other categories by using Easter as an anchor:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="663" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-663x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118224" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-663x1024.png 663w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-194x300.png 194w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-380x587.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-600x927.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-23x35.png 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-32x50.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-317x490.png 317w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-220x340.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6-385x595.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-6.png 669w" sizes="(max-width: 663px) 100vw, 663px" /></figure>



<p>Borrowing the famous <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/fashion-popup-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037726000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1nAl6t99NmE7Bd8L_ErhY9" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">fashion</a> term “complete the look,” West Elm casually invites you to check out other categories that are on sale and, hopefully, grabs your attention with one of its many offers, even if you’re not interested in its initial deal.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Run an Easter Sale</strong></h2>



<p>While the above emails are ideal for online stores that refrain from running Easter sale campaigns, this strategy is perfect for those who’re planning a holiday sale.</p>



<p>Similar to any other sales campaign, well-crafted <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/promotional-emails&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037727000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2m-yvFsZH-4wphNe1UHNeL" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">promotional emails</a> are a must-have for bringing as many subscribers back to your store as possible.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://frankandoak.com&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037728000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0g-lSh7GKwMWxzhb7dYTQ_" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Frank and Oak</a> knows this well and sends a simple, yet effective email announcing its Easter sale:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="751" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-751x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118225" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-751x1024.png 751w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-220x300.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-768x1047.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-380x518.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-600x818.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-760x1036.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-26x35.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-37x50.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-359x490.png 359w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3-385x525.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image13-3.png 798w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" /></figure>



<p>With its clean design, this email does the job: It communicates the discount level you should expect and tells how you claim it. In fact, Frank and Oak simply curates its bestsellers in this email and offers you 30 percent off them.</p>



<p>In the remainder of its email, the company features a few bestsellers you can start from and ends with a note on its egg hunt:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="767" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-767x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118226" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-767x1024.png 767w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-225x300.png 225w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-768x1025.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-380x507.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-600x801.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-760x1014.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-26x35.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-37x50.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-367x490.png 367w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-220x294.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6-385x514.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-6.png 852w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 767px" /></figure>



<p>Frank and Oak offer you an additional 5 percent off when you find the Easter eggs hidden on its website. All the more reason to click the company’s email and start browsing the sale.</p>



<p>While Frank and Oak prefer a minimalist Easter email, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.forever21.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037729000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2H79iswacxBERhtKDwiJEA" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Forever 21</a> goes all-in on email design, accompanied by the subject line “AN EGG-STRA SPECIAL SALE <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f423.png" alt="🐣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />”:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="642" height="856" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-118227"/></figure>



<p>The wordplay on the subject line aside, in this email, Forever 21 uses a colorful design with a GIF that screams Easter. The fashion retailer clearly gives its message with a bold headline that reads “50% Off”. No more copy, images, or buttons needed.</p>



<p>It’s a typical Easter email you can model if design is your brand’s strong suit.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Offer a Limited-Time Deal</strong></h2>



<p>Although <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037731000&amp;usg=AOvVaw031F-Em8a2dfVWi6cGqTfu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">discounts</a> are effective in convincing prospects to take action, they’re not the only incentives you can use around Easter. Due to their natural urgency, holidays are ideal for running <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037732000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1deYboI3ht4BFyUewmv3Iq" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">limited-time deals</a> that go beyond simple discounts. Whether it’s a free shipping code, additional gifts, or a mystery deal you want to offer, make sure to limit it by time and evoke a sense of urgency.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.eyebuydirect.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037733000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2do59O8yY6r5cIYo1EphEg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">EyeBuyDirect</a> uses this tactic smartly and couples it with a classic example of a <em>Buy One, Get One </em>offer:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="467" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-467x1024.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-118228" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-467x1024.gif 467w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-137x300.gif 137w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-380x834.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-16x35.gif 16w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-23x50.gif 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-223x490.gif 223w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-220x483.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image12-385x845.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px" /></figure></div>



<p>Sent with the subject line “Easter Looks Made Easy,” EyeBuyDirect’s email invites you to be “the best-dressed in your family group chat”.</p>



<p>The company’s approach is clever, realistic, and relatable. They know how we celebrate holidays this year, so they try to create demand for their glasses by using this angle.</p>



<p>Although EyeBuyDirect’s email does the job of promoting its limited-time offer, it could be improved with a <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/countdown-timer-popup-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037734000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1VHhd4fDXPOpg3EN4MiAw_" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">countdown timer</a>. Especially because they extended this sale, there’s almost no urgency for a subscriber to shop. (Something to consider if you’re planning to repeat EyeBuyDirect’s approach.)</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Throw an Easter Egg Hunt</strong></h2>



<p>While seasonal sales and limited-time deals are all-year-round <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-marketing-strategies&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037735000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0enevDsS1iYPkai-lbNR4v" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">e-commerce strategies</a>, there’s one little playful tactic you can only use around Easter, and that’s throwing a virtual egg hunt.</p>



<p>Don’t get me wrong, I don’t mean a full-blown <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/gamification-marketing&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037735000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1ISRQnkZy2YwHMO6Ntgk5l" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">gamified</a> online store experience. I’m talking about a simple mystery deal where you discount some of your products and position it as an Easter game.</p>



<p>Check out how <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.toofaced.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037736000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2h_4ztHvLtxascbZfpMybO" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Too Faced</a> runs an egg hunt and invites subscribers to play along via email:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="598" height="996" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118229" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8.png 598w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-180x300.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-380x633.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-21x35.png 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-30x50.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-294x490.png 294w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-220x366.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-8-385x641.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px" /></figure>



<p><br>Carrying the subject line “EASTER IS HERE! <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f430.png" alt="🐰" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />,” Too Faced’s email, first, wishes you a happy Easter and then invites you to join the hunt. With it, the company simply asks you to visit its store and find its mascot on the website. Once you find&nbsp;<em>Clover,&nbsp;</em>you can reveal your surprise and find your “Easter treat” (which is likely a discount offer.)</p>



<p>A virtual egg hunt like the above is a great excuse to invite subscribers back to your store by evoking curiosity.</p>



<p>Another brand that uses this tactic in their emails is <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.mancrates.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037737000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3cGfE-Hi0kLNQV3E2sYPri" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Man Crates</a>. Yet, the company makes it even simpler:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="737" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-737x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118230" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-737x1024.png 737w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-216x300.png 216w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-380x528.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-600x834.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-36x50.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-353x490.png 353w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-220x306.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2-385x535.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image16-2.png 749w" sizes="(max-width: 737px) 100vw, 737px" /></figure>



<p>In this digital Easter egg hunt, you hunt for Man Crates’ deals and find&nbsp;<em>egg-stra</em>&nbsp;special discounts.</p>



<p>Yes, it’s just a sale. But instead of adding a sale label to its discount products, Man Crates cleverly makes them a part of the hunt. This way, you get a sense of accomplishment when you&nbsp;<em>find</em>&nbsp;a deal and likely grab it before it’s gone.</p>



<p>In the email, the company also gives you a sneak peek at some of the deals, so you can click through and claim instantly, without even looking for them:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="872" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-872x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118231" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-872x1024.png 872w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-256x300.png 256w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-768x902.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-380x446.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-600x704.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-760x892.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-417x490.png 417w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-220x258.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6-385x452.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image10-6.png 913w" sizes="(max-width: 872px) 100vw, 872px" /></figure>



<p>It’s a quick win you can apply to your store before Easter and turn an otherwise regular sale into a virtual event, as Man Crates does.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Suggest Gift Options</strong></h2>



<p>You’re likely preparing <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-gift-guides&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037738000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2CJKZKJyq_f__hViq7iXZe" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">gift guides</a> and recommending different gift options for Christmas and <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/valentines-day-marketing&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037738000&amp;usg=AOvVaw16XTmb79UIDDO9jqzZHT3_" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Valentine’s Day</a>. What you may not be doing is repeating the same for Easter.</p>



<p>Especially during these times when we could all use an unsolicited pick-me-up, recommending gift ideas for Easter can put you ahead of the competition.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.poopourri.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037739000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0Zfft-iP8EcqCDidUSRfRW" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Poo~Pourri</a> is one of the brands that do this well:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="600" height="734" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image15.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-118233"/></figure>



<p>Written in Poo~Pourri’s typical <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/funny-email-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037740000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2FB39qetFJB9P560noAjwg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">humorous</a> tone and embellished with wordplay, this email offers you the perfect Easter gift basket for everyone on your list. What’s more, you can get 20 percent off for a limited time only and end your gift hunt.</p>



<p>In the remainder of the email, Poo~Pourri cleverly recommends gift options, divided by price for convenience:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="380" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-380x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118234" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-380x1024.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-111x300.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-570x1536.png 570w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-13x35.png 13w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-19x50.png 19w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-182x490.png 182w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-220x593.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8-385x1037.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-8.png 598w" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px" /></figure></div>



<p><br>While Poo~Pourri’s email might work well on prospects who are actively looking to buy Easter gifts, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://skandinavisk.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037740000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2RDumd1W44CmDJCao9_nJ6" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Skandinavisk’s</a> approach can make you consider gifting your loved ones, even if you haven’t thought about it before:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="645" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-645x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118235" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-645x1024.png 645w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-189x300.png 189w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-380x603.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-600x952.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-22x35.png 22w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-32x50.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-309x490.png 309w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-220x349.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4-385x611.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image11-4.png 709w" sizes="(max-width: 645px) 100vw, 645px" /></figure>



<p>Sent with the subject line “Send a gift with some extra love this Easter,” the company positions its products as thoughtful gift options with this email.</p>



<p>While doing that, Skandinavisk explains&nbsp;<em>why&nbsp;</em>you should buy gifts for your loved ones, especially this Easter. To help you even further, the company also adds a gift to your order, to make it “extra loving”.</p>



<p>Skandinavisk’s Easter email, addressed by its founder, feels personal and it successfully promotes the company’s products without sounding salesy.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Engage Your Email List</strong></h2>



<p>While a sale campaign or a limited-time deal can help activate your <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037741000&amp;usg=AOvVaw06aaCn8fH6XriFbtSw243t" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email list</a> around Easter, you don’t necessarily have to run a big sale to leverage this holiday.</p>



<p>You can engage your subscribers with an appreciative, subscriber-only discount code, or relevant, interesting email content.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://babymori.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037742000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1oXbGXx2dCAPUMSNQDEZqh" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">MORI</a> chooses the first option in this email:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="613" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-613x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118236" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-613x1024.png 613w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-180x300.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-380x635.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-600x1002.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-21x35.png 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-30x50.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-293x490.png 293w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-220x367.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2-385x643.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image17-2.png 664w" sizes="(max-width: 613px) 100vw, 613px" /></figure>



<p>In the email copy, MORI empathizes with you for how you’re likely feeling about celebrating this holiday without the whole family. The good news is, the company is giving you an extra 10 percent off just for being on their email list.</p>



<p>By “brightening their day” with a treat, MORI appreciates its subscribers and nudges them to shop for Easter.</p>



<p>If your primary goal isn’t to increase holiday sales or you don’t want to offer any discounts at the moment, you can still email your subscribers with engaging content. That’s what <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://zanzan.co.uk/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1615464037743000&amp;usg=AOvVaw13yZsuSZ0p3LqJSpNzi6iC" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Zanzan</a> does:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="679" height="1025" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118237" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8.png 679w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-199x300.png 199w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-380x574.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-600x906.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-23x35.png 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-33x50.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-325x490.png 325w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-220x332.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-8-385x581.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px" /></figure>



<p>In this email, with the subject line “A Supremely Uplifting Playlist for Easter Sunday,” Zanzan—a sunglasses company—shares a Spotify playlist they curated for you.</p>



<p>Looking at the situation through rose-colored glasses (pun intended,) Zanzan wants to remind you that better days are ahead, in case you’re feeling the holiday blues.</p>



<p>Things get even more interesting in the remainder of the email:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="523" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-523x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118238" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-523x1024.png 523w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-153x300.png 153w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-380x744.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-18x35.png 18w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-26x50.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-250x490.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-220x431.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7-385x754.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-7.png 569w" sizes="(max-width: 523px) 100vw, 523px" /></figure>



<p>Once Zanzan lifts your spirits up and gets you in the spring mood, they promote a few of its products. And it makes sense: Better, sunny days call for sunglasses.</p>



<p>It’s a clever email you can copy to engage your email list while subtly promoting your products. Best of all, it costs zero dollars.</p>


