<h2 id="h.1iy442ovbof8"><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>



<p>Not all Easter emails are created equal. Some are overly salesy, whereas others rely too much on cheesy wordplay.</p>



<p>For this post, I wanted to put together only the best Easter emails that stand out from the crowd. (Hopefully, I did a good job.)</p>



<p>Whether you’re planning to run a big Easter sale or keep it low-key this year, you can take inspiration from these 11 inventive Easter email examples.</p>



<p><em>Which of these Easter email examples is your favorite? Let me know in the comments below.</em></p>
