<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Reach a 3,800% ROI By Learning from These 6 Travel Agency Email Examples</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-117722" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Travel-Agency-Email-Examples-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_6038b39591adb" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The travel industry no doubt took a hit with COVID, and 2020 was a rough year for everyone involved.</span></p>
</div>






<p>But it’s steadily bouncing back.&nbsp;</p>



<p>In fact, the online travel market alone is expected to generate <a href="https://www.alliedmarketresearch.com/online-travel-market" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">over a trillion dollars</a> in revenue by 2022, and there’s been a CAGR of 11.1% from 2016-2022.&nbsp;</p>



<p>As lockdowns lift and restrictions ease, more and more people will resume traveling once again. I included. One of the best ways for your travel agency to reach targeted leads is through email, wherein in 2020, there was an <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/email-marketing-stats" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">average ROI of 3,800%</a>.</p>



<p>Here’s a list I’ve compiled of some of the top travel agency email examples so you can see firsthand what’s working and use those ideas to come up with your own winning formula.&nbsp;</p>


