<h2 id="1"><strong>Nassau Paradise Island</strong></h2>



<p>It’s late February as I write this. While spring is in sight and there’s a light at the end of winter’s tunnel. It’s still cold and the trees outside my office remain barren. So right about now, a tropical getaway to the Bahamas sounds pretty amazing.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/special-delivery-sunshine-inside-" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Nassau Paradise Island</a>, a travel agency that offers hotel accommodations, dining, events, and more in the Bahamas. Does an outstanding job capturing the beauty of this area and making readers feel like they’re there.&nbsp;</p>



<p>What’s interesting, however, is that this particular email was sent out right in the heart of the pandemic when much of the world was in lockdown and heavy travel restrictions were in place. So unfortunately, physically traveling to Nassau Island was out of the question for many people at the time.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But this travel agency took a creative approach where they gathered some of their favorite vacation memories from guests to help readers make the most of their “staycation.” Nassau Paradise Island also provided media like a music playlist to help readers create their own personal paradise right at home. The email starts off by asking readers, “Which way to the beach?”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117726" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-768x795.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-8.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>Then, Nassau Paradise Island offers a quick overview of what the email is about, including a well-written CTA that says, “Your Staycation Starts Here!”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117727" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-7.png 1242w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p>From there, they feature breathtaking pictures from some of their customers’ Instagram accounts.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="779" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-779x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117728" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-779x1024.png 779w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-228x300.png 228w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-768x1010.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-380x500.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-600x789.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-760x1000.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-373x490.png 373w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-220x289.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7-385x506.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-7.png 990w" sizes="(max-width: 779px) 100vw, 779px" /></figure>



<p>Beneath that, they point readers to the app they can download for sights and sounds of the Bahamas.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="782" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-782x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117729" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-782x1024.png 782w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-229x300.png 229w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-768x1005.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-380x498.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-600x786.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-760x995.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-374x490.png 374w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-220x288.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7-385x504.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-7.png 996w" sizes="(max-width: 782px) 100vw, 782px" /></figure>



<p>Finally, they wrap it up with a few more Instagram pics that create a stunning kaleidoscope of colors.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="776" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-776x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117730" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-776x1024.png 776w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-227x300.png 227w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-768x1014.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-380x502.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-600x792.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-760x1003.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-371x490.png 371w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-220x290.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7-385x508.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-7.png 988w" sizes="(max-width: 776px) 100vw, 776px" /></figure>



<p>Although the Bahamas is now open for travel, it was closed off for most of the world at the time. This travel agency email is the perfect example of how to adapt and create enticing offers regardless of what the current situation is like.</p>



<p>It’s also a visual masterpiece and shows how you can feature user-generated content to tell a story and instantly grab the attention of readers.&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/user-generated-content&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617443000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3mIVVBY_yuwi5QWENRMa2A" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Check out our guide</a>&nbsp;for more on this.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>U by Uniworld</strong></h2>



<p>Speaking of user-generated content,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.campaignmonitor.com/blog/ecommerce/2019/11/improve-email-performance-with-user-generated-content/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617445000&amp;usg=AOvVaw323SbUpyITLIxKzdD9Fulk" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">this example from U by Uniworld</a>&nbsp;who offers “modern river cruising for the active traveler” pulls this tactic off flawlessly. At the same time, they offer an ultra attractive discount that many people will find irresistible.</p>



<p>Here’s the first thing readers see&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/above-the-fold-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617446000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0djc41xz-xL8Mv7xs4QVXa" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">above-the-fold</a>.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="939" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-939x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117731" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-939x1024.png 939w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-275x300.png 275w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-768x837.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-380x414.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-600x654.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-760x828.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-46x50.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-450x490.png 450w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-220x240.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7-385x420.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-7.png 1110w" sizes="(max-width: 939px) 100vw, 939px" /></figure>



<p><br>It’s a drool worthy picture from one of the stops on “The Danube Flow” cruise that snakes its way across the Danube River in the heart of Europe, passing through Germany, Austria, Slovakia, and Hungary.</p>



<p>And just below the main image, U by Uniworld explicitly states that readers can save a whopping $500 on The Danube Flow, placing a crystal clear CTA that says, “Learn More.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="893" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-893x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117732" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-893x1024.png 893w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-262x300.png 262w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-768x880.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-380x436.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-600x688.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-760x871.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-31x35.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-44x50.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-427x490.png 427w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-220x252.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7-385x441.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-7.png 1106w" sizes="(max-width: 893px) 100vw, 893px" /></figure>



<p>When readers click on that, they can get the full details and learn how they can save a good chunk of change on their next epic adventure through the Danube.</p>



<p>It’s a straightforward delivery that allows the agency to pique the interest of readers and quickly funnels them to the page they want readers to visit. And according to research, offering a discount like this can have a huge impact on conversions—more so than many other promotions.</p>



<p>In fact, “60% of consumers prefer discounts over other types of promotional offers like rebates, free gifts, gift cards, etc.,” writes&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://jilt.com/blog/email-marketing-coupons/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617448000&amp;usg=AOvVaw30erLocVCES6s33kT-tOJL" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Max Rice</a>&nbsp;of e-commerce email marketing platform, Jilt.</p>



<p>As for user-generated content, U by Uniworld seamlessly works it in, featuring Instagram pictures and positive feedback from customers in a section called, “How Other Travelers Do U.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="891" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-891x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117733" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-891x1024.png 891w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-261x300.png 261w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-768x883.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-380x437.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-600x690.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-760x873.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-44x50.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-426x490.png 426w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-220x253.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8-385x442.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-8.png 1112w" sizes="(max-width: 891px) 100vw, 891px" /></figure>



<p>This really makes the experience come to life and gives potential customers a nice glimpse of what the Danube cruise is really like. So, by using eye-popping visuals, discounts, and user-generated content, U by Uniworld is able to get readers dialed in and seriously consider their offer.</p>



<p>I also like how succinct this email is, quickly diving into “the meat of the content,” while eliminating any superfluous information. And the black and white colors stay on brand with U by Uniworld’s website, while creating a nice contrast to pull readers in.</p>



<p>If you’re looking to offer a discount, this is a nice, simple template to borrow from.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>KAYAK</strong></h2>



<p>Travel agency and search engine, KAYAK, has become insanely popular over the last few years. I know that I’ve personally used them on multiple occasions.</p>



<p>A big part of their success is due to the level of personalization they offer—both on their website and in their emails. And I can’t stress enough just how important personalization is.</p>



<p>Just check out these stats from&nbsp;the <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.liveclicker.com/blog/21-compelling-email-marketing-and-personalization-stats-you-need-to-know-now/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617452000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0T41jA2HO1GUbdmHtRfsJq" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">real-time email marketing platform, Liveclicker</a>:</p>



<ul><li>74 percent of marketers say targeted personalization increases customer engagement rates</li><li>Personalized emails deliver 6x higher transactional rates</li><li>Segmented, targeted, and personalized emails generate 58 percent of all revenue</li></ul>



<p>Here’s what I’m talking about.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="984" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-984x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117734" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-984x1024.png 984w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-288x300.png 288w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-768x799.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-600x624.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-760x791.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-471x490.png 471w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6-385x401.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-6.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 984px) 100vw, 984px" /></figure>



<p>In this example, KAYAK sends an ultra-segmented email to a reader notifying them on an increase in flight prices based on a recent search they performed.</p>



<p>More specifically, they let the reader know that flights from Charlotte, NC to Tokyo just increased by $100. KAYAK also lets the reader know that prices may fluctuate over the next week and advise them to keep checking back or lock in a price to be safe.</p>



<p>Below that, KAYAK highlights some of the day’s top deals, along with convenient links to view all flights, as well as hotels and car rentals.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117735" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-7.png 1240w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p><br>Notice how well done the CTAs where the colors match the signature KAYAK orange and how concise they are where readers know exactly what will happen by clicking.</p>



<p>By gathering user information from previous searches on their site, KAYAK is able to send out a super targeted email featuring information the reader should have a huge interest in.</p>



<p>Not only is it extremely practical, using personalization like this can help create a tighter connection between your travel agency and readers, which can be instrumental for building long-term loyalty.</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>HotelTonight</strong></h2>



<p>“<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/let-us-upgrade-ya&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617456000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2LUOcVQlaQ2LHeEGHi0-2Q" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">HotelTonigher is a travel agency</a>&nbsp;and metasearch engine owned by Airbnb and accessible via the website and mobile app used to book last-minute lodging in the Americas, Europe, and Australia.”</p>



<p>This email specifically targets readers interested in luxe hotel deals and starts off with this jaw-dropping image&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117736" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-600x623.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-760x789.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-8.png 1226w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;and this sleek&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://sleeknote.com/blog/above-the-fold-examples&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617458000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1d7P-ZY91huhaIyrpTGzBv" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">copywriting</a>.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117737" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-7.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p><br>Very quickly HotelTonight gets readers up-to-speed on what the content of the email is about and features a simple CTA that says, “Book Luxe.”</p>



<p>Just below that, there’s a quick pro-tip that provides readers with actionable advice on how to streamline their search for luxe accommodations, including a screenshot from a smartphone.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="884" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-884x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117738" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-884x1024.png 884w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-259x300.png 259w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-768x889.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-380x440.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-600x695.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-760x880.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-423x490.png 423w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-220x255.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6-385x446.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-6.png 1114w" sizes="(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px" /></figure>



<p>I’m personally a huge fan of hacks like these, so I think it’s a cool way to educate readers, while at the same time promoting a product.</p>



<p>For the rest of the email, Hotel Tonight showcases some of their premier hotels throughout the world and features deals on some of the most noteworthy.</p>



<p>Here’s The Brazilian Court Hotel in Palm Beach, Florida with a current deal for $40 off.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="881" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-881x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117739" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-881x1024.png 881w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-258x300.png 258w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-768x892.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-380x442.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-600x697.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-760x883.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-422x490.png 422w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-220x256.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8-385x447.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-8.png 1112w" sizes="(max-width: 881px) 100vw, 881px" /></figure>



<p>And here’s the iconic Gramercy Park Hotel in New York with a deal for $66 off.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="883" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-883x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117740" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-883x1024.png 883w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-259x300.png 259w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-768x891.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-380x441.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-600x696.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-760x881.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-422x490.png 422w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-220x255.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6-385x447.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-6.png 1114w" sizes="(max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px" /></figure>



<p>The images look amazing, and offering sweet deals like this with easy to follow links is the perfect way to get readers to take instant action. At the bottom of the email, HotelTonight features a few more pictures from their Instagram feed so readers can get further inspiration to see what other types of accommodations are available.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="881" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-881x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117741" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-881x1024.png 881w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-258x300.png 258w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-768x893.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-380x442.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-600x698.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-760x884.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-421x490.png 421w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-220x256.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7-385x448.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-7.png 1106w" sizes="(max-width: 881px) 100vw, 881px" /></figure>



<p>This travel agency email example shows how you can create content around a particular theme—in this case luxe hotels—and feature relevant deals that readers are interested in. It also illustrates how powerful using the right visuals can be for captivating readers and getting them to fully explore an offer.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>Selina</strong></h2>



<p>Here’s a unique travel agency that “provides guests with beautiful places to stay, travel, and work abroad indefinitely.” In addition to offering hotel accommodations, they also offer handpicked adventures and co-working spaces. That’s why&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/leanplum-preview-hey-smiles-davis-welcome-to-selina-family&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617462000&amp;usg=AOvVaw26uNQ39E1-cIAREZq0rQ3m" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Selina has been such a hit</a>&nbsp;for digital nomads and long-term travelers.</p>



<p>This is a classic welcome email where Selina reaches out to new subscribers to explain the basics of what they offer and point out potential areas of interest on the website.</p>



<p>It begins with this fantastic image of a tropical beach with “Welcome to Selina” in bold letters for the headline, along with a brief paragraph that summarizes what readers can find.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="996" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-996x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117742" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-996x1024.png 996w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-768x789.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-760x781.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-477x490.png 477w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-9.png 1224w" sizes="(max-width: 996px) 100vw, 996px" /></figure>



<p>This is the perfect way to appeal to readers who just came on board and are trying to get their bearings. Then, Selina features two key sections of their site. There’s this one for “Explore” where readers can find an awesome adventure in premier destinations throughout the world.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="978" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-978x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117743" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-978x1024.png 978w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-286x300.png 286w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-768x804.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-380x398.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-600x628.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-760x796.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-468x490.png 468w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-220x230.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8-385x403.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-8.png 1224w" sizes="(max-width: 978px) 100vw, 978px" /></figure>



<p>Notice the clearly worded, conspicuous CTA in blue. And there’s this one for “Co-Work” where readers can find co-working spaces during their travels.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="984" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-984x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117744" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-984x1024.png 984w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-288x300.png 288w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-768x799.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-600x624.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-760x791.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-471x490.png 471w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8-385x401.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-8.png 1230w" sizes="(max-width: 984px) 100vw, 984px" /></figure>



<p>I don’t know about you, but being someone who’s personally prone to wanderlusting, this email makes me want to book my trip ASAP. So, if you’re looking for inspiration when crafting a welcome email, this is a great example to draw it from.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>Natural Retreats</strong></h2>



<p>The last of the travel agency email examples is from&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/from-12-481-ft-above-to-800-ft-below&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614331617465000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0pwehzykmMXRkAWtv1Wsoq" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Natural Retreats</a>, a brand that offers “handpicked vacation homes with well-appointed amenities in the United States’ most desirable vacation destinations.” Like the other examples I’ve listed, this one is heavy on the visuals.</p>



<p>But Natural Retreats takes a unique approach by offering infographic style content that naturally encourages readers to scroll down. It specifically promotes accommodations in Taos, NM and does so by educating readers on some of the key attractions in the area.</p>



<p>The header starts off by saying, “Why We Love Taos, NM”&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="984" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-984x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117746" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-984x1024.png 984w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-288x300.png 288w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-768x799.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-600x624.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-760x791.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-471x490.png 471w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7-385x401.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-7.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 984px) 100vw, 984px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;and then mentions the Taos Ski Valley and Rio Grande Gorge.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117747" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-8.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>Then it mentions the Taos Wilderness&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="1011" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-1024x1011.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117748" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-1024x1011.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-300x296.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-768x758.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-380x375.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-600x592.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-760x750.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-51x50.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-496x490.png 496w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-220x217.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8-385x380.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-8.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;and the Taos Pueblo.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117750" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-6.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>Each section features beautiful cartoon images and offers some interesting backstory so readers know why Taos is so special. From there, Natural Retreats offers the “5 for 4” promo code where customers can land a sweet deal on their next stay.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="994" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-994x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117751" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-994x1024.png 994w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-768x792.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-600x618.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-760x783.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-8.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px" /></figure>



<p>And for the final section, Natural Retreats highlights some specific spots to stay, featuring eye appealing images, along with property information.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117752" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-9.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>I love this email because it educates readers on the Taos area to help pique their interest and then seamlessly transitions into places to stay. The layout flows well, and using plenty of negative space between images and text keeps the content uncluttered so readers can navigate the information with ease.</p>


