										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Craft Amazing Automotive Subject Lines By Learning from These 14 Examples</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Automotive Subject Lines WordPress" class="wp-image-117685" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Subject-Lines-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_6035fd3b65010" class="block-preamble"><p class="c2"><span class="c3"><a class="c7" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.invespcro.com/blog/email-subject-lines-statistics-and-trends/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1614154300854000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2_d6WbMio5x4VdMxGfLfEf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nearly half of email readers</a></span><span class="c1"> decide whether or not to open an email based solely on the subject line. So needless to say, you need to come out swinging.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Whether you’re beginning initial outreach with new subscribers, letting readers know about updates, promoting a particular vehicle model, or anything else, your automotive subject lines need to hit their mark.</p>



<p>But to be 100% honest, this is often easier said than done. Even though it’s just a handful of words, coming up with electrifying copy for a subject line can sometimes feel like pulling teeth.</p>



<p>To make this feel like less of a Herculean effort, I’ve compiled a list of some of the most outstanding automotive subject lines in the industry today.</p>



<p>Reading through them should give you a feel of what great copy looks like, and you should walk away with plenty of inspiration to make your own subject lines sizzle.</p>



<p>Let’s jump right in.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f406d8dc96" class="block-content-upgrade">
