										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>6&nbsp;Product Launch Email Examples You’ll Want to Steal</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Product Launch Email Examples WordPress" class="wp-image-117476" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Product-Launch-Email-Examples-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_602e4ee4ee95d" class="block-preamble"><p><span class="c14">Around </span><span class="c7"><a class="c9" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://hbswk.hbs.edu/item/clay-christensens-milkshake-marketing&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808447000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3JzZXWW0ee0M1XxjcYYtME" target="_blank" rel="noopener">30,000 new products</a></span><span class="c2"> are launched each year. Unfortunately, 95 percent of them fail.</span></p>
</div>






<p>I’m not saying this to freak you out. I just wanted to put some perspective on how important it is to effectively reach your audience. Educate them when you’re unveiling a new product. &nbsp;After all,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://hbr.org/2011/04/why-most-product-launches-fail&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808448000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1wX-GWjte89uQoLKs5Ca9X" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">inadequate consumer education</a>&nbsp;is one of the fatal flaws e-commerce brands make, according to The Harvard Business Review.</p>



<p>You need to 1) get the word out at volume. 2) Help customers grasp how your product works, the features, benefits, and so on. Hands down one of the best channels to do this is email.</p>



<p>When done right, this allows you to:</p>



<ul><li>Reach an already dialed in audience</li><li>Let customers know when you’re launching a new product</li><li>Generate buzz for the release</li><li>Fill readers in on key details</li><li>Show them the value</li></ul>



<p>To get an idea of how to do this successfully. Let’s look at some next-level product launch email examples and see exactly what it is they did right.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f406d8dc96" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">Free Downloadable Bonus</p>
