<h2 id="h.2uuusfzap3v2"><strong>Table of Contents</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Willo</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Burberry</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Dims.</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Burrow</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. GoPro</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Apple AirPodsPro</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>Willo</strong></h2>



<p>Electric toothbrushes have been around for a while. But&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/your-exclusive-invite-willo-is-live-in-24hrs&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808452000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2LIvvneUsxGihyNJ1rgxkB" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Willo takes the concept</a>&nbsp;to new heights. It’s “an automated oral care robot designed to replace the toothbrush and give everyone a dynamically consistent clean.”</p>



<p>Willo uses cutting-edge technology to not just simplify toothbrushing but ensure a much deeper clean than what traditional oral care products can offer. And this product launch email does an excellent job of succinctly getting this message across.</p>



<p>Here’s the first thing a reader sees when they open it.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117478" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-6.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>There’s super&nbsp;simple yet eye-catching copy that says, “The countdown has started…” along with a picture of Willo. This instantly grabs a reader’s attention and gets them to take notice.</p>



<p>It piques their interest and creates a nice build up that makes many people want to scroll down to learn more. When they do, they see this.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="997" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-997x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117479" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-997x1024.png 997w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-768x789.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-380x390.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-600x616.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-760x781.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-477x490.png 477w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-6.png 1240w" sizes="(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px" /></figure>



<p>Willo lets readers know the product will be live in 24 hours and they’ve been chosen to receive an exclusive update. And that’s good.</p>



<p>“People like things that are exclusive,” explains&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.business2community.com/marketing/use-exclusivity-marketing-0945997&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808455000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3YcsgD-e5pO9QmzHlc23Em" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Zach Heller of Business 2 Community</a>. “They want what others covet. They want things that signal to the world that they are one of a select few. It’s in our nature as consumers.”</p>



<p>Willo also lets readers know when their e-commerce site will officially be opening and that 1,000 units will be available to their “Pioneer members.” Below that, Willo offers an “Exclusive Pioneer Code,” which allows readers to make their purchase.</p>



<p>And at the bottom of the email, there’s a brief video that offers a nice intro to the product.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117480" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-6.png 1240w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p>In just over two minutes, Willo provides a fairly detailed overview that helps readers understand the ins and outs and know exactly what separates this product from the competition.</p>



<p>You can check it out for yourself here.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-embed-handler wp-block-embed-embed-handler wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe title="Introducing Willo  |  The best clean for real people" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qNN-5OLooTY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>So, in this product launch email example, Willo effectively gets the word out and provides readers with the critical information they need without rambling on about it. The email looks great visually, and with minimal cognitive exertion, it gets leads up-to-speed, prompting many people to buy.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>Burberry</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/introducing-the-tb-summer-monogram-collection&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808458000&amp;usg=AOvVaw22WPQapSBV9VSkb7kDyTcV" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Burberry is a luxury British fashion brand</a>&nbsp;with a reputation for sleek, chic style. One of the main reasons their customers love them is because they consistently put out new collections, which are always unique and ultra fashionable. Case in point, the TB Summer Monogram Collection.</p>



<p>“A journey from reality to fantasy, the campaign blends real-life capture with a dreamlike digital world inspired by geometric skateparks and swimming pools.”</p>



<p>If you&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://us.burberry.com/tb-summer-monogram-campaign/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808459000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0z2OusaAA2H6-E8qu4thru" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">check out the collection</a>&nbsp;on their website, you’ll quickly see how innovative it is. And Burberry does a fantastic job of conveying the vibe on this product launch email example.</p>



<p>It starts off with this beautiful image of a model wearing one of the swimsuits from the collection perched on top of geometric cubes.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1009" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-1009x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117481" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-1009x1024.png 1009w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-296x300.png 296w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-768x779.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-380x386.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-600x609.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-760x771.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-483x490.png 483w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-220x223.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5-385x391.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-5.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 1009px) 100vw, 1009px" /></figure>



<p>It’s a definite attention-grabber and does a great job of &nbsp;showcasing Burberry’s newest products. Just below that, the brand gives readers a quick rundown on the launch, featuring concise copy to fill them in on the details.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117482" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-6.png 1240w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p>Burberry also uses two dead simple CTAs to instantly move readers from the email to their website.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="993" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-993x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117483" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-993x1024.png 993w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-768x792.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-600x618.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-760x783.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-5.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 993px) 100vw, 993px" /></figure>



<p>Below that, readers can take a close look at one of the most popular items from the new product line—the TB Monogram print handbag, while selecting the exact style they prefer.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1005" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-1005x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117484" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-1005x1024.png 1005w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-294x300.png 294w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-768x783.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-380x387.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-600x612.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-760x775.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-481x490.png 481w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-220x224.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5-385x392.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-5.png 1246w" sizes="(max-width: 1005px) 100vw, 1005px" /></figure>



<p>And at the bottom, readers can discover more where Burberry directs them to men’s bags, sunglasses, and women’s bags.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117485" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-768x796.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-6.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>This email is very straightforward, and with little effort readers can figure out what’s going on and why they should be interested. I love the clean, elegant design, which meshes perfectly with Burberry’s sophisticated branding.</p>



<p>I also love how they condense all of the essential information down into an easily digestible format. So, there’s much to be learned from this product launch email example.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>Dims.</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/meet-word-table-light-from-dims&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808463000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2sba3_libQkZN46_jjoj9-" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Dims. is an e-commerce brand</a>&nbsp;that sells “contemporary furnishings from the world’s top emergent designers.” Their products have a natural, modern, minimalist aesthetic that I personally love.</p>



<p>Besides their killer product line, a big part of Dims. success has been their marketing. And this email featuring the launch of a new product, the “Word Table Light” is a great example of that.</p>



<p>It’s heavy on the imagery and light on the copy — a formula that tends to work well. Here’s the first thing readers see after opening it.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="998" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-998x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117486" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-998x1024.png 998w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-768x788.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-380x390.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-600x616.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-760x780.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-478x490.png 478w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6-385x395.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-6.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px" /></figure>



<p>There’s an uber simple header saying, “Introducing Word Table Light from Dims,” followed by a clear-cut CTA of “Shop Now.” &nbsp;That’s about as straightforward as it gets, and it conveys the absolute essentials to readers with just a glance.</p>



<p>Scroll down just a bit, and readers then see the full size of the product.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="986" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-986x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117487" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-986x1024.png 986w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-768x798.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-600x623.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-760x790.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5-385x400.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-5.png 1230w" sizes="(max-width: 986px) 100vw, 986px" /></figure>



<p>Then, Dims. features another great looking image of the Word Table Light in a dark room, giving readers a feel for the atmospheric vibe it creates.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="997" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-997x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117488" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-997x1024.png 997w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-768x789.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-380x390.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-600x616.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-760x781.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-477x490.png 477w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-5.png 1242w" sizes="(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px" /></figure>



<p>This is followed by some more concise copy, which elaborates on the product and an additional CTA that leads to the same page. Dims. throws in a couple of more images in rooms with different levels of lighting&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="993" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-993x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117489" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-993x1024.png 993w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-768x792.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-600x618.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-760x783.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-5.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 993px) 100vw, 993px" /></figure>



<p><br>&#8230;and the email wraps up with some brief information about the company and what their UVP is, along with a link where readers can learn more.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117490" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-6.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>Like I mentioned before, an integral part of crafting a solid product launch email is helping customers understand your product. In some cases like Willo where there’s a lot to unpack, that means including an explainer video.</p>



<p>Other times, when a product is fairly self-explanatory, like this table light is from Dims., the best way to do that is to simply feature a handful of pictures like they did here.</p>



<p>At the end of the day, the objective is to help readers connect the dots and compel them to want to learn more. So, figure out the best way to go about that, and structure your product launch email accordingly. &nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>Burrow</strong></h2>



<p>Here’s a brand that makes “clever, uncompromising furniture and other nice things fit for modern life at home.” In this email,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/our-biggest-launch-ever-literally&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808469000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0fPXY9DVTs5tZSD8P7VRbE" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Burrow gives readers</a>&nbsp;the skinny on the unveiling of their newest product, the “Nomad Sectional.”</p>



<p>It starts off with a bang with this header and a stunning image of the Nomad.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117491" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-7.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>So, with a quick glance, readers know what’s up and can tell what the product looks like and how big it is. Directly below that, Burrow whips up some sharp copy and highlights their new product’s UVP.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117492" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-5.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p><br>The Nomad Sectional has an award-winning design and is big enough to fit the whole family. But it’s “not your grandmother’s bulky sectional sofa,” — a line I thought was extremely witty.</p>



<p>The CTA is well-placed.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117493" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-600x622.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-760x788.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-6.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p><br>And Burrow lets readers know that the Nomad Sectional is totally customizable.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117495" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-768x795.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-4.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>In fact, customers can design their own cozy corner and ensure their couch has ample seating.</p>



<p>Below that, Burrow dives even deeper into their UVP, explaining that they offer free, one-week shipping on every order so customers don’t have to deal with hassle of borrowing a truck.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="997" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-997x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117496" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-997x1024.png 997w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-768x789.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-380x390.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-760x781.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-477x490.png 477w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-4.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px" /></figure>



<p><br>I know that’s a huge selling point for me. And to cap it off, Burrow also mentions that their sectionals can easily be disassembled for customers who plan on moving.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117497" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-6.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>Here Burrow is stacking up value upon value and shows why the Nomad Sectional is more than “just another couch.”</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>GoPro</strong></h2>



<p>I think most people are&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/the-bold-new-hero8-black-is-here&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808473000&amp;usg=AOvVaw26F1tNGQSkUOC213YaJ6jS" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">familiar with GoPro</a>&nbsp;by now. They’re one of the leaders in action cameras and are used by countless vloggers to capture epic video footage.</p>



<p>One of their main strengths is their branding. They’ve managed to create massive brand equity and become the gold standard in their industry. They even have a staggering&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.instagram.com/gopro/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808474000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3YRn4RTbCHL8qpvzKwMc-8" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">17.7 million Instagram followers</a>, and counting.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="593" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-1024x593.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117498" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-1024x593.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-768x445.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-1536x889.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-380x220.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-600x347.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-760x440.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-1440x833.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-740x428.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6-385x223.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-6.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>This product launch email featuring what (at the time) was their latest product, the GoPro 8, contains all of the vital elements readers are looking for but boils it down into content that’s insanely easy to absorb.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="813" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-813x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117499" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-813x1024.png 813w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-238x300.png 238w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-768x967.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-380x479.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-600x756.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-760x957.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-389x490.png 389w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-220x277.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7-385x485.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-7.png 986w" sizes="(max-width: 813px) 100vw, 813px" /></figure>



<p>Readers can literally see everything without having to scroll whatsoever. It starts off with the GoPro logo at the top, along with a sleek looking image of the product and the number 8 so readers can instantly put it all together.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="812" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-812x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117500" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-812x1024.png 812w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-238x300.png 238w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-768x969.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-380x479.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-600x757.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-760x958.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-389x490.png 389w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-220x277.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5-385x486.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-5.png 988w" sizes="(max-width: 812px) 100vw, 812px" /></figure>



<p>This is followed by hyper-concise copy that doesn’t mince words.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="809" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-809x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117501" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-809x1024.png 809w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-237x300.png 237w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-768x972.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-380x481.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-600x760.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-760x962.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-39x50.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-387x490.png 387w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-220x279.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4-385x488.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-4.png 984w" sizes="(max-width: 809px) 100vw, 809px" /></figure>



<p>It gets straight to the point, while giving readers a brief overview of the UVP, which is “Built in mounting. Unshakably smooth video. And so much more.” Then, there’s a crystal clear CTA of “Get Yours.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="810" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-810x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117502" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-810x1024.png 810w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-237x300.png 237w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-768x971.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-380x480.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-600x758.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-760x960.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-388x490.png 388w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-220x278.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5-385x487.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-5.png 986w" sizes="(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px" /></figure>



<p>There’s no beating around the bush or long-winded spiels here. GoPro simply dives right in and gets the word out about their most recent product, providing readers with the essential information they need to know. And to find out the full enchilada, all they have to do is click-through.</p>



<p>So, if you’re looking to achieve simplicity, this is one of the best product launch email examples to base your formula off of.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>Apple AirPods Pro</strong></h2>



<p>I generally try to find examples from smaller brands because they tend to be more relatable. But&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/airpods-pro-are-here&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613650808479000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2FMkeUAE13de31XxLolyPZ" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">this final one from Apple</a>&nbsp;was so good that I couldn’t resist.</p>



<p>It was for the initial launch of their wireless Bluetooth earbuds, which were released back in October of 2019. As you would expect, the aesthetics are face-meltingly gorgeous. It starts off with a closeup of the AirPods Pro.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117503" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-6.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>Then it quickly launches into what makes them different from other products on the market. Apple starts off with silky smooth copywriting in the headline saying, “Magic like you’ve never heard.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117504" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-6.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>And then touches on the key selling points like “Active Noise cancellation for immersive sound”&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117505" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-4.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;customizable fit, a 24 hour+ listening time, sweat and water resistance, &nbsp;and transparency mode. And at the bottom, Apple points out that AirPods Pro are effortless to set up and come with a wireless charging case.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="985" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-985x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117506" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-985x1024.png 985w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-768x798.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-600x623.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-760x790.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7-385x400.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-7.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 985px) 100vw, 985px" /></figure>



<p>In terms of CTAs, they’re strategically peppered throughout here…</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117507" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-600x622.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-760x788.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-5.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;here&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1000" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-1000x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117508" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-1000x1024.png 1000w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-293x300.png 293w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-768x787.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-380x389.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-600x614.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-760x778.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-478x490.png 478w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-220x225.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5-385x394.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-5.png 1242w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;and here, seamlessly directing readers to their offers.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117509" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-600x622.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-760x788.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-6.png 1230w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p>When it comes to crafting a rock solid product launch email that fires on all cylinders and compels readers to take action, it doesn’t get much better than this example. I especially love how they broke down the main selling points into a bulleted format alongside crisp images.</p>


