										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Learn from the Best: 6 of the Top Automotive Email Examples</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Automotive Email Example WordPress" class="wp-image-117378" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Automotive-Email-Example-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_602d055170733" class="block-preamble"><p class="c5"><span class="c0">Admittedly, I’m no car expert. I can barely change a tire. I do, however, know a thing or two about automotive email marketing.</span></p>
</div>






<p>And I know how potent of a strategy it can be for automotive companies who are looking to nurture leads and set the stage for an ultimate conversion. Recent data from HubSpot also found that email engagement is on the rise.</p>



<p>In fact, “<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/email-marketing-stats&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518269000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1y7bpF2xsXnpHN2oeljbCM" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">78 percent of marketers</a>&nbsp;have seen an increase in email engagement over the last 12 months,” with 59 percent of readers saying it influences their purchase decisions.</p>



<p>The key is to craft winning emails with well-written copy and stunning visuals while concisely conveying critical messages and getting readers where they need to go.</p>



<p>To give you an idea of what that looks like, here are some of the best automotive email examples. Along with a breakdown of what they did right.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f406d8dc96" class="block-content-upgrade">
