<h2 id="h.4wefal1h752h"><strong>Table of Contents</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Subaru</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Mitsubishi</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Honda</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Infiniti</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Tesla</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Harley Davidson</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Subaru</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117382" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-768x796.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image17-5.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p><a href="https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/wait-how-many-s209-are-being-made" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">This email from Subaru</a> promotes the release of their car model the 2019 STI S209. The <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">subject line</a> reads, “Wait&#8230;how many s209 are being made?,” which instantly piques the interest of most diehard Subaru fans. And it was the limited production of this vehicle that was the focal point of the email.</p>



<p>In fact, Subaru only made 209 of them in total.&nbsp;</p>



<p>It starts off with a jaw-dropping image of the car, a catchy headline, and a clear-cut CTA that simply says, “Learn More.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117381" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-768x795.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image3-5.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>So, at a glance, readers know exactly what’s being offered, why they should care, and what action to take. In short, it helps them quickly get their bearings.</p>



<p>And best of all, this information can be found above-the-fold without having to do any scrolling whatsoever.&nbsp;</p>



<p>While you certainly don’t want to jam-pack the above-the-fold section to the point that it’s cluttered. It’s important to highlight key information so readers don’t have to do too much investigative work.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Below that, Subaru elaborates on the offer, explaining that the wait is over on this new model, and the first-ever S-line produced exclusively for the US is here.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117383" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image32-3.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>Then, they feature another sexy image of a blue model of the S209 and mention the starting price. This is followed by the same “Learn More” CTA&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117384" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-768x796.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image33-3.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;and they wrap it with yet another beautiful image and listing a few additional benefits, which really crystallizes the UVP of the email.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117385" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-768x796.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image28-3.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>So, if you’re looking to promote a new car that’s coming out, this is one of the perfect automotive email examples to draw inspiration from.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Mitsubishi</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="982" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-982x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117386" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-982x1024.png 982w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-288x300.png 288w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-768x801.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-380x396.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-600x625.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-760x792.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-470x490.png 470w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3-385x401.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image34-3.png 1228w" sizes="(max-width: 982px) 100vw, 982px" /></figure>



<p>Next, there’s this email from Mitsubishi, which has three main objectives.</p>



<ol><li>Show off and promote the Pajero Sport</li><li>Share some practical automotive tips with readers</li><li>Promote their 100 Years of Adventure Sale</li></ol>



<p>To begin, Mitsubishi places an epic looking picture of the Pajero Sport climbing up a craggy rock face above-the-fold. It’s a beauty and immediately grabs readers’ attention and makes them want to explore more.</p>



<p>Just below that, Mitsubishi features a video, which lets readers see straight up what the Pajero Sport looks like in action, and is followed by some crisp copywriting that specifically targets adventure lovers.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="986" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-986x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117387" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-986x1024.png 986w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-768x798.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-600x623.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-760x790.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5-385x400.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image16-5.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 986px) 100vw, 986px" /></figure>



<p><br>So, with minimal cognitive lifting, Mitsubishi gets readers up-to-speed on their core offer. From there, they include two informative, educational sections.</p>



<p>One is on how to tackle a tow&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117388" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-600x622.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-760x788.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image4-5.png 1230w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p>…which includes another video to check out.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117389" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image31-4.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>The other is on how to pack for adventure trips&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117390" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image19-5.png 1240w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;which features a link to their six-step packing guide.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="997" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-997x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117391" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-997x1024.png 997w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-768x789.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-380x390.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-600x616.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-760x781.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-477x490.png 477w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image22-5.png 1242w" sizes="(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px" /></figure>



<p>Known as education content marketing, sharing knowledge and helpful tips like this can be a winning strategy.</p>



<p>Experts have found that it’s huge for developing stronger rapport, trust, and brand loyalty.</p>



<p>It’s also a great way to show that you know your stuff and are an authority in your industry. &nbsp;</p>



<p>After that, Mitsubishi talks about their 100 Years of Adventure Sale&#8230;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117392" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image12-5.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>&#8230;and features a few different vehicle models.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="773" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-773x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117393" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-773x1024.png 773w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-226x300.png 226w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-768x1018.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-380x504.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-600x795.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-760x1007.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-26x35.png 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-370x490.png 370w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-220x292.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3-385x510.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image29-3.png 984w" sizes="(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px" /></figure>



<p>This is one of the best automotive email examples I’ve seen because it does such a great job of unpacking a lot of information into a straightforward email format that’s easy to digest.</p>



<p>There’s a strong visual component, which nearly all great emails have, with short, “snackable” sections that readers can quickly browse through.</p>



<p>Without overwhelming anyone, Mitsubishi covers a lot of ground and uses simple CTAs, pointing readers to the pages they want them to visit.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Honda</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="938" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-1024x938.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117394" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-1024x938.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-300x275.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-768x703.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-380x348.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-600x550.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-760x696.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-38x35.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-55x50.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-535x490.png 535w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-220x202.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5-385x353.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image14-5.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/type-r-back-on-pole-position&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518284000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1DJPayo-RdBqhOdFbm8AXn" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">This email from Honda</a>&nbsp;is an absolute masterpiece. It reminds me more of a movie advertisement for a summer blockbuster than it does a traditional automotive email.</p>



<p>Just check out the face-melting images and riveting headlines promoting the Honda Civic Type R. &nbsp;At the top, above-the-fold, Honda starts off with a breathtaking picture of the vehicle, five stars, and the simple yet potent headline of “What Car.”</p>



<p>This helps get readers immediately dialed in, compelling them to scroll down to learn more. When they do, they see this quick copy that gets them up-to-speed on the purpose of the email.</p>



<p>Honda explains that they “gave a few lucky motoring journalists the chance to experience the brand new Type R around a test track in Dresden” and include a straightforward CTA for readers to check out the reviews.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="794" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-794x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117395" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-794x1024.png 794w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-233x300.png 233w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-768x991.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-380x490.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-600x774.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-760x981.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-39x50.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-220x284.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6-385x497.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image15-6.png 992w" sizes="(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px" /></figure>



<p><br>Then, they launch into more brief yet powerful quotes from some of those publications.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="901" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-901x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117396" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-901x1024.png 901w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-264x300.png 264w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-768x873.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-380x432.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-600x682.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-760x864.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-31x35.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-44x50.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-431x490.png 431w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-220x250.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6-385x437.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image5-6.png 1116w" sizes="(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px" /></figure>



<p>And just look at how mesmerizing the combination of images and reviews are.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="891" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-891x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117397" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-891x1024.png 891w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-261x300.png 261w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-768x883.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-380x437.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-600x690.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-760x873.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-44x50.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-426x490.png 426w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-220x253.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4-385x442.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image23-4.png 1112w" sizes="(max-width: 891px) 100vw, 891px" /></figure>



<p>They really pop, and anyone who’s even remotely interested in the Honda Civic Type R can’t help but get excited.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="895" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-895x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117398" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-895x1024.png 895w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-262x300.png 262w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-768x878.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-380x435.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-600x686.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-760x869.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-31x35.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-44x50.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-428x490.png 428w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-220x252.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4-385x440.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image30-4.png 1114w" sizes="(max-width: 895px) 100vw, 895px" /></figure>



<p>I especially love this last review from&nbsp;<em>The Telegraph&nbsp;</em>that calls it “the British-built Godzilla.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="890" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-890x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117399" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-890x1024.png 890w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-261x300.png 261w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-768x884.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-380x437.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-600x690.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-760x875.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-426x490.png 426w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-220x253.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5-385x443.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image18-5.png 1114w" sizes="(max-width: 890px) 100vw, 890px" /></figure>



<p>Just below that, Honda inserts the “Find Your Dealer” CTA, letting readers conveniently find a location near them where they can find the Type R.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="887" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-887x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117400" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-887x1024.png 887w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-260x300.png 260w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-768x886.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-380x439.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-600x692.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-760x877.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-425x490.png 425w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-220x254.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4-385x444.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image21-4.png 1116w" sizes="(max-width: 887px) 100vw, 887px" /></figure>



<p>And at the very bottom, they promote the hashtag #honda25, along with links to their social media accounts.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="916" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-916x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117401" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-916x1024.png 916w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-268x300.png 268w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-768x859.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-380x425.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-600x671.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-760x850.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-31x35.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-438x490.png 438w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-220x246.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4-385x431.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image26-4.png 1116w" sizes="(max-width: 916px) 100vw, 916px" /></figure>



<p>This is honestly one of the most eye-catching automotive email examples I’ve come across and shows that bold aesthetics combined with simple but catchy copywriting is a magical formula. And it’s one that you can replicate as well.</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Infiniti</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="993" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-993x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117402" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-993x1024.png 993w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-768x792.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-760x783.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image2-5.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 993px) 100vw, 993px" /></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/be-driven-by-inspiration&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518290000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3mlOI2kvazMbofkB9ED2pX" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">This one from Infiniti</a>&nbsp;is the shortest example on this list, which makes it perfect for reaching mobile users — something that’s important given that “<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/email-marketing-stats&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518290000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2sfxnSuw8qnyMuXjan8Zxp" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">mobile opens account for 46 percent</a>&nbsp;of all email opens.”</p>



<p>It starts off with a fantastic headline of “Be driven by inspiration. Build your new Infiniti Q70 Luxury Sedan.” And there’s a jaw-dropping image of this car model that evokes a sense of elegance and sophistication that Infiniti is clearly going for.</p>



<p>Beneath that, there’s a short section that goes over the highlights of the offer, along with a CTA directing readers to download the brochure. There’s also a second image of the Q70 Luxury Sedan on a contrasting white background, giving readers a better sense of the subtle details.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117403" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-600x622.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-760x788.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image20-4.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p>The third and final part of this email is this section where readers learn about the $10,000 cash back bonus Infiniti is offering, and find links to the various sections of the website.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="986" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-986x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117404" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-986x1024.png 986w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-768x798.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-380x395.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-600x623.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-760x790.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-220x229.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5-385x400.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image11-5.png 1230w" sizes="(max-width: 986px) 100vw, 986px" /></figure>



<p>For instance, there’s a link where readers can learn how to build their own Infiniti, compare models, view inventory, and more. Everything flows together nice and smoothly on this example, and it proves that you don’t need a long-winded spiel to have an impact.</p>



<p>In fact, less is usually best, especially when your goal is to reach mobile users.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Tesla</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1003" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-1003x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117405" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-1003x1024.png 1003w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-294x300.png 294w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-768x784.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-380x388.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-600x613.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-760x776.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-480x490.png 480w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-220x225.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5-385x393.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image8-5.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 1003px) 100vw, 1003px" /></figure>



<p>Although&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/tesla-august-updates&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518294000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3kN2QeESgc2fRu0wzAbpxg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">this email from Tesla</a>&nbsp;is a little old from 2015, there’s still plenty you can learn from it.</p>



<p>The crux of the content is to highlight some of Tesla’s major updates from that period, and they get right down to business with this ultra clear headline.</p>



<p>They start off explaining the upgrades they made to the Model S, including adding a more robust battery pack, increasing range by 6 percent, and improving acceleration by 10 percent.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="992" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-992x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117406" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-992x1024.png 992w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-768x793.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-600x619.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-760x785.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image25-4.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px" /></figure>



<p>Note that it’s always smart to use quantifiable numbers like these whenever possible because it helps readers get a sense of the value you’re offering. Rather than saying, this new model is faster, for example, saying acceleration has improved by 10 percent is far more effective.</p>



<p>Below the copy, Tesla includes three CTAs of “Read More,” “Design Yours,” and “Test Drive” to efficiently point readers to the right section of their website. Notice how clear these CTAs are and how they leave no room for misunderstanding.</p>



<p>Next, Tesla has this section on the economic advantages of electric cars, where they explain how drivers can save big money long-term by making the switch.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1000" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-1000x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117408" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-1000x1024.png 1000w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-293x300.png 293w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-768x787.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-380x389.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-600x615.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-760x778.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-478x490.png 478w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-220x225.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4-385x394.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image13-4.png 1240w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure>



<p><br>Again, they use plenty of concrete numbers, and like Mitsubishi did in a previous automotive email example, Tesla is incorporating customer education into their marketing mix.</p>



<p>As I mentioned before, education is empowering for customers and helps them make more informed buying decisions. So, always be on the lookout for ways to educate and pass on your knowledge.</p>



<p>For the rest of the email, they feature additional information on the Model S, highlighting the core benefits and pointing readers to helpful resources where they can learn more.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="879" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-879x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117409" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-879x1024.png 879w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-257x300.png 257w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-768x895.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-380x443.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-600x699.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-760x886.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-420x490.png 420w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-220x256.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4-385x449.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image10-4.png 1112w" sizes="(max-width: 879px) 100vw, 879px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117410" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-292x300.png 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-600x617.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image9-4.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p>I like this email because it’s super informative and helps potential customers navigate the car buying waters. It also has a nice layout with plenty of white space so readers can seamlessly scroll to find the specific details they’re looking for.</p>



<p>So, if your goal is to provide your audience with updates, this is an excellent formula to follow.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Harley Davidson</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="995" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-995x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117411" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-995x1024.png 995w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-768x790.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-380x391.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-600x618.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-760x782.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-476x490.png 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-220x226.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6-385x396.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image24-6.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px" /></figure>



<p>My final automotive email example is&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://reallygoodemails.com/emails/day-2-of-deals-luggage-motorcycle-covers-more&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518299000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3ALjfIlC09NP0H2zeUXhrC" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">from Harley Davidson</a>&nbsp;and takes a different approach than the others I’ve mentioned so far.</p>



<p>Rather than promoting vehicles, it promotes gifts and accessories.</p>



<p>Sent out during the holidays of 2017, this email starts off with a crisp headline of, “The gift bag that rides with you,” which is followed by two conspicuous CTAs for “Shop All Deals” and “Find a Dealer.”</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="994" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-994x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117412" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-994x1024.png 994w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-291x300.png 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-768x792.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-380x392.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-600x618.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-760x783.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-49x50.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-475x490.png 475w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-220x227.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5-385x397.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image7-5.png 1238w" sizes="(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px" /></figure>



<p>Piggybacking off the subject line, “Day 2 of Deals: Luggage, Motorcycle Covers + more,” this email helps readers quickly get their bearings and figure out exactly what Harley Davidson is offering here.</p>



<p>Then, it transitions into highlighting two specific types of accessories — luggage and motorcycle covers.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="989" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-989x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117414" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-989x1024.png 989w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-768x795.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-600x621.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-760x787.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image27-3.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 989px) 100vw, 989px" /></figure>



<p>There are great looking images, and Harley also includes pricing information, ensuring total transparency right from the start.</p>



<p>I don’t know about you, but I hate having to guess how much something costs and do a bunch of sleuthing on my own. And many other people feel the same, which is why it’s always nice to include pricing info whenever possible.</p>



<p>After that, Harley features four gift sections with crystal clear CTAs so readers know precisely what’s being offered and the action they need to take.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="987" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-987x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117415" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-987x1024.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-289x300.png 289w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-768x797.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-600x622.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-760x788.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-472x490.png 472w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5-385x399.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image6-5.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure>



<p><br>Lastly, there’s this section where they have a link to all holiday gifts, a free gift with a $300 purchase, dealer information, and free shipping with a $50 purchase, plus free returns.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="990" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-990x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-117416" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-990x1024.png 990w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-768x794.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-380x393.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-600x620.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-760x786.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-474x490.png 474w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4-385x398.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/image1-4.png 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></figure>



<p>Everything is laid out smoothly, and the color scheme of this email perfectly matches Harley’s signature black and orange. And that’s really important because having consistent brand presentation across different channels can boost revenue by&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.forbes.com/sites/gabrielshaoolian/2018/08/10/10-marketing-web-design-branding-statistics-to-help-you-prioritize-business-growth-initiatives/?sh%3D34713a42d708&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518303000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3EzWbQwNK5ulkyrBf35yZQ" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">as much as 23 percent</a>.</p>



<p>“Every piece of collateral—from social media channels to website designs to product packaging—should maintain a similar color scheme, tone, overall aesthetic, and communicate a similar message that fits your brand identity and core values,” writes&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.forbes.com/sites/gabrielshaoolian/2018/08/10/10-marketing-web-design-branding-statistics-to-help-you-prioritize-business-growth-initiatives/?sh%3D34713a42d708&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1613566518304000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0d3HjmZMIueqJDjMZifoUN" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Gabriel Shaoolian of Forbes</a>.</p>



<p>So, if you’re looking to bring exposure to gifts and accessories and make smaller sales, this template from Harley Davidson is a good one to follow.</p>


