<div id="preamble-block_60081cbff0b23" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">First impressions are everything—in real-life and with </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">email marketing</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Create a strong connection right out of the gate and you set the stage for solid reader engagement, click-throughs, and conversions. And in many cases, this knocks down the first domino for building loyalty and getting repeat business.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But how do you make sure you make a great first impression? Simple. With a compelling welcome message. Here’s everything you need to know about creating one, along with several welcome message examples for ideas and inspiration. </p>


