										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Permission-Based Email</strong> <strong>Marketing: Why It’s Important (and Examples of Brands That Do it Well)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Permission-Based Email Marketing [WordPress]" class="wp-image-115906" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Permission-Based-Email-Marketing-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_6000438bb1bd3" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Permission-based </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing"><span style="font-weight: 400;">email marketing</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, simply put, is where you initiate email communications only after someone has consented to receive content from you. </span></p>
</div>






<p>It’s the opposite of using non-permission-based tactics like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/buy-email-list">buying an email list</a> or cold emailing people off of social media.&nbsp;</p>



<p>You can think of it as the “up-and-up” approach to email, and it’s vital for not only staying on the good side of readers but for maximizing conversions.&nbsp;</p>



<p>For this post, I’ll give some specific reasons why permission-based email marketing is important and show you what it looks like in action, offering multiple examples from brands that truly get it.</p>



<p>Let’s not waste any time.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f406d8dc96" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">Free Downloadable Bonus</p>
